{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"23":{"eng-name":"Commercial Transactions (Kitab Al-Buyu)","ara-name":"كتاب البيوع"}},"section_detail":{"23":{"hadithnumber_first":3326,"hadithnumber_last":3415,"arabicnumber_first":3326,"arabicnumber_last":3415}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3376,"arabicnumber":3376,"text":"حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو بَكْرٍ، وَعُثْمَانُ، ابْنَا أَبِي شَيْبَةَ قَالاَ حَدَّثَنَا ابْنُ إِدْرِيسَ، عَنْ عُبَيْدِ اللَّهِ، عَنْ أَبِي الزِّنَادِ، عَنِ الأَعْرَجِ، عَنْ أَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ، أَنَّ النَّبِيَّ صلى الله عليه وسلم نَهَى عَنْ بَيْعِ الْغَرَرِ - زَادَ عُثْمَانُ - وَالْحَصَاةِ ‏.‏","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Muslim (1513)"}],"reference":{"book":23,"hadith":51},"chapter":{"id":25,"ara-name":"باب فِي بَيْعِ الْغَرَرِ","eng-name":"Regarding Transactions Involving Ambiguity","isFirstHadith":true}}]}